<author>hrmạs smyr w d/ rmsys zky, hrmạs smyr w d/rmsys zky</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉ḥbk fḥbk .. yʿjz fyh ạlklạm
 ạ̉ḥbk fṣlbk .. sẖfạny bạltmạm
 ạ̉ḥbk fqrbk .. sbạny fy hyạm)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉ḥbk yạ sydy .. lạ ạ̉kẖrj ḥraⁿạ
 wnạrk fy dạkẖly .. tsbyny lk ʿbdaⁿạ)2
 2- (ạ̉ḥbk lsẖkẖṣk .. yạ sydy ạlqdyr
 ạ̉ḥbk wnyrk .. hyn ly ysyr
 ạ̉ḥbk wsẖkrk .. fy ṣdry ạ̉syr)2
 3- (ạ̉ḥbk fạ̉nt ly .. sẖhyq dẖy ạlḥyạẗ
 ạ̉ḥbk fḥbk .. qlby qd ạ̹sẖthạh
 ạ̉ḥbk fdmk l.. ạ̹tẖmy qd mḥạh)2</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉ḥbk fḥbk</title>
</song>